#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-lepidoptera-sampling.adoc:68
msgid "Some national offices use groups of volunteers to digitize the paper logs and produce digital spreadsheets.  The spreadsheets are very simple and include three datasheets.  One captures the information linked to the sampling efforts, the second the weather conditions and the third the species encountered and the number of individuals observed by the amateur."
msgstr "部分國家辦公室使用志工團隊來數位化紙本紀錄並製作數位試算表。這些試算表非常簡單，共包含三個資料表：第一個記錄與調查活動相關的資訊，第二個記錄天氣狀況，第三個記錄業餘愛好者觀察到的物種與個體數量。"

