msgid "What data structure would you use to reflect the data in these logs?"
msgstr "你會使用什麼資料結構來呈現這些紀錄中的資料？"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-lepidoptera-sampling.adoc:85
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-practice.adoc:71
msgid "Create a spreadsheet using this structure and the data from the logs."
msgstr "請使用此結構和紀錄中的資料建立試算表。"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-lepidoptera-sampling.adoc:94
msgid "Taking the role of one of the volunteers with advanced computer skills, imagine you have been assigned the responsibility for data quality issues.  Your main task is to reduce the amount of data that is currently discarded (around a 15%) before processing due to errors and inconsistencies.  You have received a dataset as the raw product of the digitization effort."
msgstr "假設你是具有進階電腦技能的志工之一，負責資料品質管理問題。你的主要任務是減少目前因錯誤和不一致而在處理前被丟棄的資料量（約 15%）。你收到了一個數位化工作的原始資料集。"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-lepidoptera-sampling.adoc:96
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-practice.adoc:84
msgid "Download xref:attachment$UC2-LS-3-ForCleaning.xlsx[UC2-LS-3-ForCleaning.xlsx]. (44 KB)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-lepidoptera-sampling.adoc:98
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-marine.adoc:106
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-practice.adoc:86
msgid "Identify possible ways to correct those issues, and perform those corrections for as many of the errors present as you can."
msgstr "找出可能的修正方式，並盡可能修正其中的錯誤。"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-lepidoptera-sampling.adoc:107
msgid "For this exercise, you will take the role of the taxonomic expert collaborating with IBAN at their headquarters.  Some of your previous responsibilities (writing the annual report, and producing the base distribution maps) have been handed over to the volunteers, and you have now been given a new responsibility: publishing the cleaned data online through the GBIF network.  The volunteer in charge of data quality has provided a dataset to be published."
msgstr "在這個練習中，你將扮演與 IBAN 總部合作的分類學專家。你先前的責任（撰寫年度報告和製作基礎分布地圖）已經交給志工，而你現在有了新的責任：透過 GBIF（全球生物多樣性資訊機構）網絡在線上發布已清理的資料。負責資料品質管理的志工已提供了要發布的資料集。"

